Help on skill:     Wild strike
Usage duration:    random
Fatigue:           high
Skill type:        attack
Affecting stat(s): strength, dexterity, intelligence, attack, weapon skill, anatomy and spot weakness

The typical spellblade is far from a martial master, relying on magic to gain the upper hand. As such, their training in melee techniques leave much room for improvement. This one in particular is a most basic attack, executed quickly
and usually with a distinct lack of skill. But it is often heavily augmented with magic, making the attack something to be wary of.
This attack can only be executed with daggers, swords, polearms, or bladed or piercing ancients.
